  "bio_raw": "She is a highly enthusiastic lecturer with five years of experience in higher education. Currently teaches as a Lecturer of History at General Education Department at the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh. She is able to deliver informative lectures effectively on subjects through engaging her students. Her taught subjects are History of the Emergence of Independent Bangladesh and Bangladesh Studies. She possesses strong communication and interpersonal skills with a passion for fostering intellectual growth among students.",
